{"tid":2110513,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"想同個已婚女同事傾幾句，但她好似連早晨都唔多想講","createTime":"2020-07-16T03:27:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T05:35:44.000Z","uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8d14739c89a1ef90a9089eac0dff1d371715c0c4","tid":2110513,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T03:27:57.000Z","msg":"有個已婚的女同事，之前都會同我講早晨，但近日只是苦笑左了一下就算。<br />\n<br />\n可能她只和她隔離的女同事食飯，這女同事對我印象麻麻地，或者對我有不滿就同呢個女同事講，令這女同事有戒心。<br />\n<br />\n我因公司坐位安排坐在另一邊，時會到這兩位女同事坐的地方影印，亦會借機望兩眼，可能係坐附近的2條八婆見到我留意這女同事就有意無意同這女同事講。<br />\n<br />\n這個已婚女同事係良善的婦人，不愛是非，勤勤力力做好每日工作外，她只是同我打一次招呼，其他時間唔會理我或其他同事。對我來說有點失望。"},{"pid":"0c20393f7e48937af53fa0717d457b14b7fc467c","tid":2110513,"uid":216704,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T03:28:55.000Z","msg":"jm9..."},{"pid":"0bd55e4a1a33217e9ef98e7d262cb3172c80bdbb","tid":2110513,"uid":73381,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c20393f7e48937af53fa0717d457b14b7fc467c","tid":2110513,"uid":216704,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T03:28:55.000Z","msg":"jm9..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T03:31:16.000Z","msg":"最衰這兩條八婆"},{"pid":"e0ccc18780c1cfe0348c980eefe78da8dafc2380","tid":2110513,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:41:42.000Z","msg":"皇后？"},{"pid":"8fbb56d630048bd3cd4ede61888adcb737105908","tid":2110513,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e0ccc18780c1cfe0348c980eefe78da8dafc2380","tid":2110513,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:41:42.000Z","msg":"皇后？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:50:19.000Z","msg":"皇姑。。。"},{"pid":"b842e5bffd9fc33bc27c5622a0fc6b114bb3da43","tid":2110513,"uid":21267,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:52:49.000Z","msg":"樓主屎眼爆炸而死"},{"pid":"19e2b6059f6d9a08a6aa90fa5a7689506f387501","tid":2110513,"uid":360830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pi